<div class=3D"CalloutBox" style=3D"box-sizing: border-box"><h3 style=3D"tex=
t-align: center">Fabric Count Quick Tip</h3>
<p style=3D"text-align: left;">If you stitch over 2 threads on 28-count eve=
nweave or linen, treat as 14-count Aida.</p><p style=3D"text-align: center;=
"><b>Remember to leave enough for framing!</b></p><p style=3D"text-align: c=
enter;"><a href=3D"https://www.needlework-tips-and-techniques.com/embroider=
y-fabric.html">Why fabric count matters</a></p>
</div>
