<h2>IMPORTANT: Before You Cut Your Fabric!<br></h2>
<ul><p>The calculator only shows the size of the stitched area. Allow extra=
 for finishing.</p></ul><ul><li><b>Cards</b>: add =E2=89=A5 1 in / 2.5 cm m=
argin on all sides</li><li><b>Framed pieces</b>:&nbsp;add =E2=89=A5 3 in / =
7.5 cm margin on each side to allow for mounting, wraparound and framing.</=
li></ul>
<h2>No more tears?</h2>
<p>No more frustrated hoop flinging! Get it right first time, and enjoy you=
r project without worrying.</p><p>Keep the link to this page somewhere safe=
, not hidden in that huge bookmark list you never return to.&nbsp;</p>
